Interface Signature.TypeArg

All Known Subinterfaces:
Signature.TypeArg.BoundedPREVIEW, Signature.TypeArg.UnboundedPREVIEW
Enclosing interface:
SignaturePREVIEW
public static sealed interface Signature.TypeArg permits Signature.TypeArg.UnboundedPREVIEW, Signature.TypeArg.BoundedPREVIEW
TypeArg is a preview API of the Java platform.
Programs can only use TypeArg when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.
Models the type argument.
